node.text: Being a Rainbow ball is not easy! You have places to be, people to meet... and ice cream to buy! 😄 Watch our first animated series to find out who's to blame when you lose a level!

node.text: The second part of the Lunar New Year story has arrived! 🎉 Will the villagers be able to protect their homes from the beast? What will the mysterious old man say to the scared people? 😳 Find out in our exclusive video!

node.text: Lunar New Year is approaching! Delve into the story of this mysterious holiday with this unique video our Chinese team prepared for you! Any ideas how the story ends?

node.title: Homescapes: The Story of Lunar New Year, Part 1

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Homescapes on August 04, 2021 tagging @gardenscapes_mobile, @farmscapes_mobile, and @wildscapes_game. May be a cartoon of cat and text that says 'wA scapes'.

Photo by Homescapes on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Plan for today 4 am: wake up and feed the screaming Cat 5 am: fall asleep 8 am: wake up and feed the Cat. Again. 8:30: breakfast! 9 am: water the flowers 10 am: order new furniture 1 pm: make coffee, feed the Cat & play Homescapes! 2 pm: continue renovating the room 5 pm: pet and feed the Cat 6 pm: read the Superbutler graphic novel 10 pm: fall asleep while playing Homescapes'.
